WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.740
No, I don't want it.

2
00:00:02.740 --> 00:00:05.790
She doesn't want to.

3
00:00:05.790 --> 00:00:06.790
What about I?

4
00:00:06.790 --> 00:00:07.790
She told you.

5
00:00:07.790 --> 00:00:08.789
Oh, God.

6
00:00:08.789 --> 00:00:11.789
I've worked hard to train you over the years.

7
00:00:11.789 --> 00:00:12.789
And this is how you repay me?

8
00:00:12.789 --> 00:00:14.789
It's not much money to have this.

9
00:00:14.789 --> 00:00:15.789
I want to sacrifice.

10
00:00:15.789 --> 00:00:16.789
In a grave.

11
00:00:16.789 --> 00:00:18.789
I built you and this company.

12
00:00:18.789 --> 00:00:19.789
I pay love for it.

13
00:00:19.789 --> 00:00:20.789
The controller.

14
00:00:20.789 --> 00:00:21.789
The name of love.

15
00:00:21.789 --> 00:00:23.789
I am your father.

16
00:00:23.789 --> 00:00:25.789
How can you say such things?

17
00:00:25.789 --> 00:00:28.789
It seems in this house it's no room to tell truth.

18
00:00:28.789 --> 00:00:30.789
I will never return here.

19
00:00:49.390 --> 00:00:51.390
Why didn't you tell me to let it stop?

20
00:00:51.390 --> 00:00:53.740
I don't know.

21
00:00:53.740 --> 00:00:55.740
If I tell you that she didn't let me.

22
00:00:55.740 --> 00:00:57.740
Is it enough reason for you?

23
00:00:57.740 --> 00:00:59.740
I don't even know this person.

24
00:00:59.740 --> 00:01:05.769
Everything what I can think about is the person from your past that you cared about.

25
00:01:05.769 --> 00:01:08.150
It's your relationship with me.

26
00:01:08.150 --> 00:01:10.150
Not to be a supervisor.

27
00:01:10.150 --> 00:01:11.859
No.

28
00:01:11.859 --> 00:01:13.859
I may really fall in love with you.

